0세였고, 그녀의 어머니 Adela von Vohburg(은)는 30세였다. 그녀는 Guillaume II Count de Chalon-sur-Saone(와)과 적어도 한 명의 딸을 두었다. 그녀는 대략 1174년 프랑스 부르고그니 사o니-트-로이르 차론-수-사o니에서 23세의 나이로 사망했으며 독일 바데-wu르테버그 오스탤브크레이스 로르치에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"1152–about 1174":"1152. gads–ap 1174. gadu","1152–1174":"1152.gads–1174","1140–1202":"1140–1202","1096–1171":"1096–1171.gads","1170–1227":"1170–1227","1122–1190":"1122–1190","1122–1187":"1122–1187","1190":"1190","1187":"1187","1152":"1152. gads","1174":"1174","1096":"1096","1140":"1140","1171":"1171. gads","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","um 1170":"ap 1170. gadu","1147":"1147. gads","1202":"1202","1122":"1122","about 1174":"ap 1174. gadu","Chalon-sur-Saône, Saône-et-Loire, Burgundy, France":"Chalon-sur-Saône, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne, Francija","Thiers, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"Thiers, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, Francija","Duchy of Swabia, Holy Roman Empire":"Heiliges Römisches Reich","Lorch, Ostalbkreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Lorch, Ostalbkreis, Baden-Württemberg, Vācija","Germany":"Vācija","Vohburg, Nordgau, Holy Roman Emplire":"Holy, North Ayrshire, Skotija, Lielbritānija"},"mg":{"1152–about 1174":"1152–tany ho any amin'ny 1174","1152–1174":"1152–1174","1140–1202":"1140–1202","1096–1171":"1096–1171","1170–1227":"1170–1227","1122–1190":"1122–1190","1122–1187":"1122–1187","1190":"1190","1187":"1187","1152":"1152","1174":"1174","1096":"1096","1140":"1140","1171":"1171","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","um 1170":"tany ho any amin'ny 1170","1147":"1147","1202":"1202","1122":"1122","about 1174":"tany ho any amin'ny 1174","Chalon-sur-Saône, Saône-et-Loire, Burgundy, France":"Chalon-sur-Saône, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne, Frantsa","Thiers, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"Thiers, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, Frantsa","Duchy of Swabia, Holy Roman Empire":"Heiliges Römisches Reich","Lorch, Ostalbkreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Lorch, Ostalbkreis, Baden-Württemberg, Alemana","Germany":"Alemana","Vohburg, Nordgau, Holy Roman Em